  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279">
        <l>yākā</l>
        <l>piṟapiṟak karōpō māteṉa varūu</l>
        <l>māyēḻ collu macainilaik kiḷavi.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref
          target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/169/mode/1up">
        169</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, acaikkum iṭaiccoṟkaḷait tokuttu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
</p>

      <p>
        varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘yā paṉṉiruvar uḷarpōlum māṇākkar akattiyaṉārkku’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa, yā vantavāṟu kāṇka.
      </p>
      <p>
        kā:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘utukā’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa varum.
      </p>
      <p>
        piṟa:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit3">
        <l>‘atupiṟa, itupiṟa, utupiṟa’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉap piṟa vantavāṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit4">
        <l>‘atu piṟakku’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉap piṟakku vantavāṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit5">
        <l>‘koṭiyuvaṇattavarō’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa arō vantavāṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit6">
        <l>‘piriyēṉ vāḻēṉ pōteyya’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉap pō vantavāṟu;
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit7">
        <l>‘nīrpō nērikai pukaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉpatum atu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Ilam-cit8">
        <l>‘viḷintaṉṟumātavatteḷintaveṉ ṉeñcam’</l>
        <trailer>[naṟṟi-178]</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉa mātu vantavāṟu.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref
          target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n219/mode/1up">216</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n220/mode/1up">217</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        i - ḷ. yā mutalākiya ēḻiṭaiccollum acai nilaiyām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        u.m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit1">
        <l>yāpaṉṉiruvar māṇākkaruḷarakattiyaṉārkku.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘puṟaniḻaṟ paṭṭāḷō vivaḷivaṭ kāṇṭikā.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit3">
        <l>‘tāṉpiṟa varicai yaṟitaliṟ ṟaṉṉun tūkki.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit4">
        <l>‘atupiṟakku.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit5">
        <l>‘nōtaka viruṅkuyi lālumarō.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit6">
        <l>‘piriyiṉ vāḻā teṉpō teyya’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Cena-cit7">
        <l>‘viḷintaṉṟu mātavart teḷintaveṉ neñcē.’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e-m. varum.
      </p>
      <p>
        iṭam varaiyaṟāmaiyiṉ ivai mūṉṟiṭattiṟkumuriya.
      </p>
      <p>
āṅkavum oppilpōliyum uraitoṭaṅkuṟaṟkaṇṇum ātaramilvaḻiyum varutaliṉ, vēṟu kūṟiṉār.	(31)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/303/mode/1up">303</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/304/mode/1up">304</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        acainilaic coṟkaḷ.
      </p>
      <lg>
        <l>yākā,</l>
        <l>piṟapiṟak karōpō māteṉa varūum</l>
        <l>āyēḻ collu macainilaik kiḷavi.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
iḳtu, acainilai kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        (i-ḷ.) yā kā piṟa piṟak karō pō māteṉa varū um āyēḻ collu macainilaik kiḷavi ― yā, kā, piṟa, piṟakku arō pō mātu eṉṟu colla varukiṉṟa avvēḻu collun tāñcārnta collai yacaittu niṟkum nilaimaiyaiyuṭaiya collā meṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘yā paṉṉiruvar māṇākkaruḷa rakattiya ṉārkku,’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <p>
        iṉṉum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit2">
       <l>‘tōḻiyā cuvākatam pōtu kīṅkeṉa’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        veṉṟu pāṭamāyi ṉatuvu mitaṟ kutāraṇam.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit3">
       <l>‘puṟaniḻaṟ paṭṭāḷō vivaḷivaṭ kāṇṭikā’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit4">
       <l>‘tāṉpiṟa</l>
       <l>‘varicai yaṟitaliṟ ṟaṉṉun tūkki’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit5">
       <l>‘nacaitara vantōr nacaipiṟak koḻiya’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit6">
       <l>‘nōtaka</l>
       <l>‘viruṅkuyi lālu marō’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit7">
       <l>‘piriyiṉ vāḻā teṉpō teyya’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Nacc-cit8">
       <l>‘viḷintaṉṟu mātavart teḷintaveṉ</l>
       <l>neñcē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉavum varum. <num xml:lang="en">(31)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref
          target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n186/mode/1up">
        179</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
        i-ḷ: ― yā mutalākac collappaṭṭa ēḻu collum acainilaik kiḷaviyām. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
        u-m:― yā ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit1">
        <l>“tōḻiyā cuvarkkam pōtukiṅkeṉa”</l>
        <!--(cīvaka. 1021)-->
      </lg>
      <p>
kā ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit2">
        <l>“puṟaniḻaṟ paṭṭāḷō vavaḷivaṭ kāṇṭikā”</l>
        <!--(kali. 99)-->
      </lg>
      <p>
piṟa ― tāṉ piṟa ― 
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit3">
        <l>“varicai yaṟitaliṟ ṟaṉṉun tūkki.</l>
        <trailer>(puṟam-1<num rend="traditional">40</num>)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
piṟakku ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit4">
        <l>“nacaipiṟak koḻiya”.</l>
        <!--(puṟam. 15)-->
      </lg>
      <p>
arō ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit5">
        <l>“nōtaka, viruṅkuyi lālumarō.</l>
        <trailer>(kali 33)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
pō ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit6">
        <l>“piriyiṉ vāḻā teṉpō teyya”.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
mātu ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC279-Tey-cit7">
        <l>“viḷintaṉṟu mātavat teḷinta veṉṉeñcē.</l>
        <trailer>(naṟ-178)</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa varum.	(30)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
